Listening to this show tonight reminded me why I fell in love with the music 20 years ago.  I was at these shows and I was there tonight. I Thank you for the pristine sound quality...and I thank God for a good ear.

Come on now, Cringle...."Even a blind man knows when the sun is shining."

Warlocks Show As many will know, this is the most heralded of the two famous "Warlokcs" shows from East Coast Fall Tour '89.  This show is completely amazing, especially Dark Star and the haunting Death.  Anything less than five stars for this one is a joke.
